Menu
class Represents a complete menu Has name and price.
PartyItem
Represents a component of a party such as menu, decoration or something else needed to organize a party Has name/description, price and can be either of adult or child type
PartyPlanner
A main class which holds list of decorations and menus for party planning and a party Plan which is created by choosing options from those lists
Plan
Represents a party plan consisting of: number of guests (adult and children) menus for adults and children (one or both) and a decoration for the party
StandardUser
Defines a set of methods every standard user needs to implement

Used to define if menu or decoration is for adults or children
UserType
A standard USER can plan a party by choosing options: number of guests (adults and/or children), menus and decorations An ADMIN user can manage available menus or decorations
